{"tid":265821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（有片）正妹露奶 咸濕猴又扯衣又渣波","createTime":"2017-06-01T03:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-14T09:29:32.000Z","uid":41351,"like":40,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e25bce85c3c178041d9282c2e89003dd1a94cad2","tid":265821,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:22:42.000Z","msg":"強國猴秒變「奶襲哥」　對正妹扯衣偷桃<br />\n中國河南一處觀光景點，日前有場猴戲表演，並讓現場觀眾和猴子拍照。其中一名正妹姐姐和猴子拍照時，猴子竟然當場變「奶襲哥」，還拉扯正妹姐姐的衣服。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據中國《梨視頻》報導，猴子在表演後準備和這名妙齡女子合照，而女子一度低身露出乳溝，散發出母性的光輝。這隻猴子也忍不住直視，甚至一度變成「奶襲哥」，對女子偷桃襲胸，還拉扯女子的衣服，也讓女子受驚。不過女子還是繼續保持笑容，與猴子開心合照。（施旖婕／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/A2s8LS58f6k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FA2s8LS58f6k&d=tdfcCaI%2BvaIn3erCU8nExMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=14fc0751\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/A2s8LS58f6k</a><br />\n猴子：大家係男人，點忍"},{"pid":"dbefc00ac41c4ad6d6c361460c6d7cefe02d34c3","tid":265821,"uid":41351,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:23:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/01/112318_137fd65d0427408e015939b78bb22580.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F01%2F112318_137fd65d0427408e015939b78bb22580.jpg&h=f946337c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人靚波甜"},{"pid":"6d804225a4e640c5d062b83d52ef6c53bf374618","tid":265821,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:25:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e5dbcfea818c75cfad8d7bb586e66a7c0851bb5","tid":265821,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:27:54.000Z","msg":"台灣都出過「猴抓妹」：佢更獲出版社邀請，推出性感寫真集 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d43a5925056cb5694988252b28f0cd2dab13b81f","tid":265821,"uid":33162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:33:01.000Z","msg":"41j <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif